    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors achieve required level. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3, accepted given medium model risk and corroborating dual-laboratory experimental data. Uncertainty quantification performed via Monte Carlo propagation of material and geometric input distributions; all three QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and percentage difference < 10%. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
